ivardefs.name: active
ivardefs.desc: Indicates whether the record for the group is available for use or is merely being retained for historical purposes.

ivardefs.name: actual
ivardefs.desc: If true, indicates that the resource refers to a specific group of real individuals.  If false, the group defines a set of intended individuals.

ivardefs.name: characteristic_
ivardefs.desc: Identifies traits whose presence r absence is shared by members of the group.

ivardefs.name: code
ivardefs.desc: Provides a specific type of resource the group includes; e.g. "cow", "syringe", etc.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: A unique business identifier for this group.

ivardefs.name: managingEntity
ivardefs.desc: Entity responsible for defining and maintaining Group characteristics and/or registered members.

ivardefs.name: member_
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the resource instances that are members of the group.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: A label assigned to the group for human identification and communication.

ivardefs.name: quantity
ivardefs.desc: A count of the number of resource instances that are part of the group.

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: Identifies the broad classification of the kind of resources the group includes.

properties.desc: Represents a defined collection of entities that may be discussed or acted upon collectively but which are not expected to act collectively, and are not formally or legally recognized; i.e. a collection of entities that isn't an Organization.
